text: Rajab Moqbil (born 1959) is a Saudi Arabian former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Saudi Arabian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Saudi Arabia Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
